---

**Summary**

These exhibits reveal a progressively deteriorating relationship between Card Connect and Shift4, culminating in heated language ("spiritual warfare") and accusations. The text messages, in particular, showcase the very personal and combative nature of the dispute from the perspective of Jared Isaacman. The theoretical'd, examples portions of Exhibit 22 provide context surrounding the termination of referrals. The specific use of "spiritual warfare" in multiple conversations indicates a highly charged, personal dimension to the business conflict.
